  "translations": {
    "en": "In the name of Allah, Most Merciful. From the slave of Allah, Amirul Mu'mineen, Ali ibn Abi Talib, to the people of Egypt and Muhammad ibn Abu Bakr. I convey to you my praise for Allah, other than Whom there is no god.",
    "ur": "بسم اللہ الرحمن الرحیم۔ اللہ کے بندے امیر المؤمنین علی بن ابی طالب کی طرف سے اہل مصر اور محمد بن ابی بکر کو سلام۔ میں اللہ کی حمد بیان کرتا ہوں جس کے سوا کوئی معبود نہیں۔",
    "tr": "In the name of Allah, Most Merciful. From the slave of Allah, Amirul Mu'mineen, Ali ibn Abi Talib, to the people of Egypt and Muhammad ibn Abu Bakr. I convey to you my praise for Allah, other than Whom there is no god.",
    "fa": "In the name of Allah, Most Merciful. From the slave of Allah, Amirul Mu'mineen, Ali ibn Abi Talib, to the people of Egypt and Muhammad ibn Abu Bakr. I convey to you my praise for Allah, other than Whom there is no god.",
    "id": "In the name of Allah, Most Merciful. From the slave of Allah, Amirul Mu'mineen, Ali ibn Abi Talib, to the people of Egypt and Muhammad ibn Abu Bakr. I convey to you my praise for Allah, other than Whom there is no god.",
